{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b3588b2bde","title":"对薄一波关于上海三反五反情况和部署的报告的复电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c69894b84","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":29,"articleId":"b3588b2bde"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"e7fe33abea","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3588b2bde","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"薄一波，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任、中央人民政府节约检查委员会主任，受中央委派在上海帮助三反五反工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"dd6783c352","type":"title","text":"对薄一波以关于上海三反五反情况和部署的报告的复电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3588b2bde"},{"id":"e7fe33abea","type":"paragraph","text":"薄一波同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3588b2bde"},{"id":"f98a3aa238","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十七日的电报收到。你和华东局、上海市委诸同志共同决定将上海五反停止下来到三月二十号再行发动的方针及各项处置是完全正确的。这样既有利于现在的三反，也有利于三月二十号以后的五反，也有利于全国的经济形势。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3588b2bde"},{"id":"852d729af0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3588b2bde"},{"id":"6ce5a9e0ad","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十九日上午一时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3588b2bde"}],"page":{"id":"51f32e66b8","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3588b2bde","start":452,"end":452}}}},"__N_SSG":true}